Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shrine maiden...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.38,0:00:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shrine maiden...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.06,0:00:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Be silent, yomotsu okami!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16}yomotsu okami can be translated to "ancient, great deity"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Be silent...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.86,0:00:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why am I the only one who has to suffer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Must I endure this pain alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.66,0:00:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why only me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you have been abandoned, yomotsu okami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It is only because you have betrayed yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Preposterous!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.26,0:00:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The great one did not complete me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:01:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at that damned land.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nowhere for you to go in that world of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.02,0:01:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do it? Why is it that you protect this place?\NThis unfair world that was created?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.11,0:01:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.16,0:01:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Izanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I caused great pain to your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a disdainful wish that scarred your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, I have had unpleasant\Nfeelings toward myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you must bear great hatred toward me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be... untrue.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For everything as with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.39,0:01:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why you fought so boldly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I... believed that you would create something grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Izanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am disappointed as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:01:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Izanagi... sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.61,0:02:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of me not as a lowly\Nmaiden, but as a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Izanagi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Izanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I propose this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Within my body I have a place of masculinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Within your body you have a place of femininity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to join my place of masculinity\Nwith yours of femininity within us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In which we will create the lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I do. I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Izanami! Izanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Izanagi-sama. Inzanagi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Izanagi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Life...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}HEroAP Presents
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Indigo Magatama
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki Touma (18 yrs.)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru Touma (19 yrs.)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, I don't do well in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, jii-chan's always tough like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do I have to practice this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokusuke Touma
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,For 2025 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people would just say 2000\Nyears when they joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,More like, it didn't seem like a joke at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, Miyuki, if you really feel like always\Nsaying such things, I'll cut you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be better for you to pay\Nyour own way through school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then you can cook for\Nyourself starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes a lot of effort to make food every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be better to cook for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll only cut off Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami Minase (18 yrs.)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They look like... they're a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Miyuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan, about this thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I can't bring myself to give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Some girls have confessed to him too,\Nbut I heard they were all rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think onii-chan wants to\Ngo out with anyone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I think for now you should just continue to\Nbe good friends with him, Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're right. Thanks, Miyuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, good morning, Hikaru-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure working hard this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you over your insomnia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say that you literally\Ncouldn't sleep for three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And it looks like you wrote a love letter there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I wonder what kind\Nof guy Nanami-chan likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I told you it's not a love letter, senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan. didn't you have an English\Ntest or something today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? There is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I reminded you over and over last night, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Cra - I didn't have a clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Took you long enough, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagisa Kurashima (19 yrs.)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were avoiding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My astounding swordsmanship versus\Nyour old, decrepit swordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is better... We're settling it all today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute, Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to deal with that this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an English test today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,T-E-S-T!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Touma's in the fight now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I put five on Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all for Kurashima to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm rooting for Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's all Kurashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you not struggle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I want to struggle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you just say you weren't up to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I'm not just going to let you win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My win, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your underwear's in plain sight, Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You peeping... bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:09:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan! Wake up! Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagisa-san, you're horrible! Hitting him so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you always smack him around too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's different since we're siblings!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, more importantly, shouldn't we\Nbe getting him to the nurse's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, we should.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kanaka, help me out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Great one, please help our people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A noble kyuuseishu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,To save us in our time of need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayaka Tachibana
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake, Hikaru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ayaka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you just had a shock to the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Ayaka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, at school you have to\Ncall me Tachibana-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this questionable setup?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been forever since I've been with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayaka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're turning red.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure you don't have a fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're just being shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Hikaru-chan? You're acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve been in the bath together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You mean when I was just a little kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And Miyuki was with us too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru was so cute back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not even listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hey, hey, why does your chest stick\Nout like that? Can I touch it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember you said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You were pretty bold back then, Hikaru-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to try touching them again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh good, senpai's already awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,See? He's alive all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...that she was jealous of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would she say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what she could ever\Nbe jealous of about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're horrible! What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She said that she was jealous that\NI had such a good older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, did she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, just tell her that I'm available\Nto be her brother whenever she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's... with the angry tone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,198!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,199!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,200!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't any ordinary dream, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... Nanami-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,With onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan! You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16}The word "kyuuseishu" can partially be translated with words like savior or messiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyuuseishu-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyuuseishu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who I am destined for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumo Academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.14,0:15:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This classroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That dream again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. jii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there some girl who wants me at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, where did that come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering since I had a weird dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it had a girl dressed as a shrine maiden...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dressed as... a shrine maiden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What, ojii-chan? Do you know what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but... Izumo Academy has a\Nlot of tremors going around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to talk to the board chairman\Nabout any spiritual-related things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, say...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,l-ls there someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...that you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about Nanami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanam-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Nagisa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Or Ayaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Or even that shrine maiden you saw in your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think... of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What... about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you can't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,After all. I'm just your sister, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Don't ask me such weird questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot something. I'm going back for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, be sure to catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here. No doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two - !!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nagisa! What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The place I study is in this direction,\Nand this way's shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And what might you be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Swinging your bokutou wildly like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Nagisa. Do you believe in ghosts or spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.91,0:18:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this classroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't there anything in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What a weird room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something under there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A stone doorway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that doing under the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,An earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:19:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like an alter, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You made it upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Another earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! Run for it, Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell are you groping me, pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks like the place we came in...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It think so too, but, what is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.93,0:21:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone! Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagisa-san! Help me down from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on my way to my club, then\Nthere was this earthquake...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then everything turned white around me.\Nand when I woke up I was up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.21,0:21:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have any tact?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:21:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's got my legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.73,0:21:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.49,0:22:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.22,0:22:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.17,0:22:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.08,0:22:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.96,0:23:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.13,0:23:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.34,0:23:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.46,0:23:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.55,0:23:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.89,0:23:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.35,0:24:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.65,0:24:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we the only ones that didn't make it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.19,0:24:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And then that alter...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.28,0:24:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No good. I can't get anything on my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.03,0:24:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.58,0:24:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.83,0:24:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I thought I heard something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.13,0:24:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ayaka sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.42,0:24:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.50,0:24:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All the way through that earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.84,0:24:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.39,0:24:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if you've gained a little weight...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.73,0:24:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sensei!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.32,0:24:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No good, everything around us has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.57,0:24:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try to find another town.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.61,0:24:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll run into something past that forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.03,0:25:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot something. I'll catch up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.95,0:25:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki, please be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.55,0:25:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.72,0:25:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Kaede...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.97,0:25:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the jyorogumo that you fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.22,0:25:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs16}"Jyorogumo" Is the Japanese word for Nephila clavata. a species\Nof golden orb-web spider that is quite common in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.22,0:25:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the jyorogumo that you fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.56,0:25:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Jyorogumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.69,0:25:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,and now I’m at quite a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.28,0:25:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.53,0:25:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What I mean is, I'll like for you\Nto take me as my new master.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.28,0:25:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.74,0:25:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I have no clue what you're talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.83,0:25:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.96,0:25:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.71,0:25:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a dream. Only a dream, Hikaru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.16,0:26:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.04,0:26:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.00,0:26:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so good, Hikaru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.77,0:26:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaede-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.98,0:26:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I need you to spread your essence inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.96,0:27:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.12,0:27:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your energy's inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.58,0:27:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Our destinies are now entwined, my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.09,0:27:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I A dream?
